---
title: Italian Chicken Tray Bake with Mashed Potato & Green Beans
description: Use your oven to create a dish brimming with flavour! Baking chicken with veggies all in one tray results in a saucy and delicious medley that's perfect for mopping up with creamy mashed potatoes. Add some beans for your green fix, and this colourful plate ticks all the boxes!

*Each week, we search the country to source the best ingredients, with a focus on quality and variety. This week's cherry tomatoes were in short supply, so we've replaced them with gourmet tomatoes. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
